item.description:
Do you want to take your power back from events and situations happening in your life that you don't want to happen?

Do you want to know how to start creating and manifesting more rapidly than before?

Do you want to know that what you want is on its way with no doubt?

Do you want to feel more empowered to be all that you are here to be?


We will be covering and discussing one of the powerful processes called the Art of Deliberate Creation...

A whole book has been written on this topic.

Come learn, participate and start attracting your dreams from a vibrational standpoint...

This process involves pre-planning and preparation but once you've mastered the skill, it becomes second nature and all kinds of wonderful things you've been waiting for begin to show up in your life's experience.

Connect with powerfully positive like minded people who will support and encourage you on your journey. It will be fun

And as always, a door prize is raffled off for those who come
